rgin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;但美国的任何战略收益都更难以辨别。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;伊朗对袭击的回应是关闭了该海峡，禁止&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/1awAcifXzh_ZvUHqgF5lRXYJS06h3ywwidKV9Tw3YT6jcKcwkqMtJ8BNUoFO8aP1X0n0yi5BPRlMb1TS8jqUTWgoteCzrGDC56Iy0NUNENBxzN4Cqh5ubB1_y2-fQgAXnEhSUvaqgNx0-NyrQH49uOA6kNcJaM-zU06-hT_acAfI3Gfj8hTyTtgeOAfepHgvxI4LRgGfWi8tCDqQpljwDXVZVugqDqXwXH4gxV5TCVqdv7P9wmXByToVyqp1Ix2GWR1SHayhLh7lJZ2UMOkIEwh8UshK20FDYK9eBR1B6HnVZS_YyWx9aZmul1-LFFUkcz1q-4Dt6WtHGF9JirmYI-6xCYupctd9EMlEi5gGSGGbs8OPi67Uvw-hzX-x3Trwx4b6VBbqNr55gIPxJVOivFO9AIxsvQNl8Y18O6QJitBjbCrIHWMpB8j7jTk7fvT9dMhqtNNXU6I0mTlHDe-Rp_wFe9RCrxrlQeH9YMeu8Y3Z7Lf0TuAi0w0_BYKoLNJN-kSeM8m-NQyv9y1t9pcMdw4XjCu3sugl7BAxFzmSQMsIyw/Yypjg3MCxqG4LehZQv1oORdszh593uMJ/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗制定了霍尔木兹过境程序，但船东持谨慎态度"&gt;几乎所有航运&lt;/a&gt;——这基本上是史无前例的——并向沙特阿拉伯、阿拉伯联合酋长国和其他美国海湾盟友发射导弹和无人机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;能源成本飙升是令特朗普头疼的一大问题，美国汽油价格目前处于&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/nAp7gyiFar7mTOEN-roe8cdOz6G4YLHSBX1uTef2ywbUy16-LfXP2IaSuO3vcvtBAKvCMo1riCgtOi73NIw6s2zOnuG39dpxAEN7vm9mn_tMLhqLI3jXUcVOol4Gxs_eZS-JXhkQNFsIkCRY_3T4uLyzMYKmAE_6RdZr-fDEhZtcv9cuLqU4c0Ktd1tx5PjfpRymsIByq1MCQ62ZU6KL8RPJKnr5bbKGDI7tUIsIlzgPIA3evJyKngMVjwsK7w1P5YIT7IV98rHA2GQmDRxhYtt29z3NZCv6aeRHDPrJATug6bi3qTSHKJ2PL8foCx3jIQp7cEURUxyltp43aWf-k0jIYTEWKsZMGSRfNZ7jjmiYYgpijScsWRAvZFpUBZnZx5C_VuSlqYLxrSHhiOFszFEHruzU4eVAoyFaOzwa5LEQI10nSHMo_RCo4S529XwJBM82drzM0n2iAkt7vP2s8iMj-pyIlrlttkLp9w_u9_r_grkqsrPjSBQRQjzBEpd3scZVKvUeCetwdsYV9IcLMfnMKqA-encXlhkFoTRvGLXQ4ghwyA/8BfjUl1ZIwc_3hJZJbaXeZK_aedF7L_n/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗燃油紧缺加剧，美国汽油价格触及 4.50 美元，接近历史新高"&gt;2022年以来的最高水平&lt;/a&gt;。美国选民越来越反对战争，而欧洲、非洲和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/q2zrQF4L9dhOYX2Vedx8udU-3Eq7Yg5NdegDRBQQ-R3SrCyvAW9rdYnRgMH1mv-NTcn8ZI