" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="卢拉直视特朗普，为巴西赢得关税胜利"&gt;走上了一条熟悉的钢丝&lt;/a&gt;：在不升级紧张局势的情况下保持坚定。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;如果过去的经验有任何指导意义的话，政治老手会让这一切看起来很容易。&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;—&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/NE4NqlCg4Ipy9DBE0IUOuiHzFtuU6L0wva4_CBDX3j2DqQsFpkl3bkV5X7Nar6HGIa95r-R8cEGreVoePKjP_IMGU8LF5b7KZhS9TrBf52yhP2KMSR0OOJS6xUFNOoh-yGdsyKakap2E4Q_632OEt_quUMG-VGmkoG6hDs48jEkrLAkDpbw1_aQZfNFgPiYrrhlJyhWl1Sy840vzO3wy3tNtjbjFdUcQICM-U00gcJgOL4TB2UkpkHX753u36wzhRpK2_c9ZME9dVh_H7bKdHGOrAt8ipIfuOCLCS8A3F3RFk_ydrq1dc0iQsYH5ZScavD_xunaERY3mYw/4OkJsPUtFyV68mGfgvrjLqvzJumSyNZH/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="Daniel Carvalho - 拉丁美洲生态政府记者 |彭博社"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;丹尼尔·卡瓦略&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWOf_0xz3wsw/v10/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva, Brazil&amp;amp;#39;s president, arrives for a ceremony to commemorate three years since an attempted coup, at Planalto Palace in Brasilia, Brazil, on Thursday, Jan. 8, 2026. Brazil&amp;amp;#39;s Supreme Court last September sentenced Jair Bolsonaro to 27 years and three months in prison for plotting a coup after his 2022 election defeat, making him the first former president convicted of such a crime in a nation long scarred by successful and failed power grabs. Photographer: Ton Molina&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2026 年 1 月 8 日星期四，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦抵达巴西巴西利亚普拉纳尔托宫，参加未遂政变三周年纪念仪式。去年 9 月，巴西最高法院因贾尔·博尔索纳罗在 2022 年选举失败后策划政变而判处 27 年零 3 个月监禁，这使他成为首位被定罪的前总统在一个长期因成功和失败的夺权而伤痕累累的国家，发生了这样的罪行。摄影师：Ton M